{
    "is_good_patch": true,
    "synth_pr": "\n## Title: Implement UE Context Modification Refuse Handler\n\n### Summary\nThe UE context modification failure handling was incomplete in the OAI5G codebase. There was dead code in `CU_handle_UE_CONTEXT_MODIFICATION_FAILURE` that just asserted, and the corresponding `ue_context_modification_refuse` function was missing in the MAC layer. This caused failures during UE context modification to be silently ignored or crash the system.\n\nThe fix implements the missing functionality to properly handle UE context modification failures by:\n1. Replacing the assertion in `CU_handle_UE_CONTEXT_MODIFICATION_FAILURE` with actual message processing\n2. Adding the missing `ue_context_modification_refuse` function in the MAC layer\n3. Connecting all the components with proper function pointers and message definitions\n\n### Changes\n- `openair2/COMMON/f1ap_messages_def.h`: Added `F1AP_UE_CONTEXT_MODIFICATION_FAIL` message definition\n- `openair2/F1AP/f1ap_cu_ue_context_management.c`: Implemented `CU_handle_UE_CONTEXT_MODIFICATION_FAILURE` to process F1AP failure messages\n- `openair2/LAYER2/NR_MAC_gNB/mac_rrc_dl_handler.c`: Added `ue_context_modification_refuse` function implementation\n- `openair2/LAYER2/NR_MAC_gNB/mac_rrc_dl_handler.h`: Added function declaration\n- `openair2/LAYER2/NR_MAC_gNB/mac_rrc_ul.h`: Added `ue_context_modification_refuse_func_t` type definition\n- `openair2/LAYER2/NR_MAC_gNB/nr_mac_gNB.h`: Added function pointer to UL interface structure\n- `openair2/RRC/NR/mac_rrc_dl.h`: Added `ue_context_modification_refuse_func_t` type definition\n- `openair2/RRC/NR/mac_rrc_dl_direct.c`: Initialized function pointer in direct init\n- `openair2/RRC/NR/mac_rrc_dl_f1ap.c`: Added F1AP wrapper function and initialized function pointer\n- `openair2/RRC/NR/nr_rrc_defs.h`: Added function pointer to DL interface structure\n- `openair2/RRC/NR/rrc_gNB.c`: Added handler for F1AP modification failure message\n\n"
}